data.description: Nestled in a fantastic neighborhood, this charming bungalow-style home boasts FOUR bedrooms and 1.5 baths! As you enter the front door, you're greeted by a bright, inviting living room flooded with natural light. The eat-in kitchen adjacent to the living area is adorned with laminate flooring. The kitchen has ample cabinet space and essential appliances, including a range, microwave, and fridge, making meal preparation a breeze. You'll discover two bedrooms on the main floor, each offering a unique charm. One bedroom features classic hardwood flooring, adding warmth and character; the other provides plush carpeting for comfort. Completing the main level is a full bath featuring a single vanity and a convenient tub shower kit. Venturing upstairs, you'll find two additional spacious bedrooms. You can utilize these well-appointed spaces to suit your lifestyle, whether an office space, playroom, or further guest bedrooms. The unfinished basement offers potential for expansion or customization according to your preferences. Additionally, it features a convenient half bath and walkout access to the backyard, providing seamless indoor-outdoor living. Step outside and discover a haven for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. The fully fenced-in yard offers privacy and security, while two sheds provide ample storage space for outdoor equipment and tools. An above-ground pool beckons on the upcoming warm summer days, offering a refreshing retreat. And a patio provides the perfect spot for outdoor dining, barbecues, or simply soaking up the sun. The home is conveniently located just minutes from parks, shopping centers, and schools. Don't miss your chance to see this wonderful home; schedule your showing today! (On the main floor, hardwood is underneath the carpet. updates include roof-2023, fence-2020, AC-2019, furnace-2018, and siding-2023)
